{"tid":2066913,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蕭若元：中國不會收回國安法，法例非常嚴厲，會送中判死刑。有BNO既要即走，否則走唔到","createTime":"2020-06-16T15:18:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-16T16:08:45.000Z","uid":28114,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"912e48c42eae3fc3b323286679290236d6d63eb0","tid":2066913,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T15:18:01.000Z","msg":"蕭生：「啱啱英國內政大臣寫咗封信比首相同國家安全委員會主席，要求佢喺17號9點回覆。 內容指關於BNO搵嘢做既計劃章程係需要時間寫，所以而家請求你明日九點前答覆並且授權俾BNO者一去到希斯羅機場就俾佢逗留。<br />\n<br />\n呢件事咁緊急反映佢哋已經收到風中國係不會收回國安法，而且法例非常嚴厲，最近放出嚟嘅風聲係大陸要掌握全部調查、起訴，甚至送返大陸法庭審理，判處死刑。預計喺月底之前就會通過國安法。 所以佢哋預計條例一出，有BNO既短期之內就要走，否則等佢實施之後就走唔到。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/MeIMj0y75jo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FMeIMj0y75jo&d=St%2FdMm9ieZWtYGJEeV6aaxZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=f66a3166\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/MeIMj0y75jo</a>"},{"pid":"52b0a3de4887271e7e0281eb186fab626b7d4b3d","tid":2066913,"uid":17641,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T15:20:01.000Z","msg":"解讀:中國會收回國安法，法例得啖笑，會發大財。有BNO既唔使走<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58e4d24e2b4cefcb24202594b436ff2046df7fdb","tid":2066913,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T15:22:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"889a6c486b1a28c783f4b875cf422779605e757d","tid":2066913,"uid":2117,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"52b0a3de4887271e7e0281eb186fab626b7d4b3d","tid":2066913,"uid":17641,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T15:20:01.000Z","msg":"解讀:中國會收回國安法，法例得啖笑，會發大財。有BNO既唔使走<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T15:24:37.000Z","msg":"衲dee心水清<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmo